Request the number of results for a query

Source: R/methods_base_request.R
query_nresults.Rd

Request the number of results for a query

Usage

query_nresults(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An <int> vector

...

Additional arguments

Value

An <int> vector

Examples

care_endpoint("care_enrollees") |> query_nresults()
#> NULL
care_temporal("quality_payment") |> query_nresults()
